details.sectionContent: Perfect place where you play with virtual currency.
If you really wants to challenge your risk taking ability and your luck.This event is absolutely for you.
In this round, the participants have to collect various types of objects from the given location. The objects list will be given on the spot.
In this round, the participant of a team have to blind bet on his/her teammate that the teammate can able to complete the dare.
In this round you will be provided with fake cash and you will have to buy fake guns from us. Person who buys the best guns with more money left with him will be the winner
